cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with the problem of license plate detection and recognition in natural scene images, which is a classic computer vision problem. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a unified deep neural network for this task, which involves training the network end-to-end. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed approach on three datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the category cs.MM (Multimedia).
